Class OraFeatureExtractionSettings

All Implemented Interfaces:
javax.datamining.base.BuildSettings, javax.datamining.MiningObject, oracle.dmt.jdm.OraPLSQLConstants
public class OraFeatureExtractionSettings
extends OraBuildSettings

OraFeatureExtractionSettings object encapsulates the following build settings specific to feature extraction.

  • Number of features to control the maximum number of features that can be extracted by the model. The default value is computed by the DME using heuristics that depend on the number of columns and rows in the input data.
See Also:
